@crux_capital_ Good map. I'd add $SOI to Layer 1. 
Soitec makes the Photonics-SOI substrates that most of this stack depends on. 95% market share. No volume alternative qualified at the foundries that matter.
Currently evaluating whether the market has priced that in or just started to.

@TraderBillyAU Little higher to go until oil settles lower

That’s dragging the dollar down giving plenty of lift to risk bullshit

Catch me in photonics how-bout-dat https://t.co/vt2yqv7JRW

